        <Parent_String>screens in Christian religious buildings [300265151], Christian religious building fixtures [300003724], religious building fixtures [300003723], architectural elements by building type [300078071], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
